dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Burnett County WI, 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Burnett County, Wisconsin in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Burnett_Hydro_2018.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'BURNETT_HYDRO_2018_LINE' and 'BURNETT_HYDRO_2018_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
